.

1. *Zovi* me u 8 uveče. (Call me at 8 o'clock in the evening.)
2. Ona je *zvala* svoje prijatelje. (She was calling her friends.)
3. *Zove* me svaki dan. (He calls me every day.)
4. Ona će *zvati* te sutra. (She will call you tomorrow.)
5. *Zvao* sam te juče. (I called you yesterday.)
6. *Zvali* smo ga na rođendan. (We called him on his birthday.)